ck win that demands respect.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"precisely the kind\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"spirited comeback win\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 279}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But let today\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s discussion be about the defeated player.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"today\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s discussion\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"the defeated player\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For this match\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094that, fittingly, ended in a third-set tiebreaker\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094marks the end of Kerber\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s career, a run as estimable as it is instructive.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"match\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094that\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"a third-set tiebreaker\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094marks\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerber\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s career\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a swell life being a mid-tier tennis player.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a swell life\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"a mid-tier tennis player\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s financially lucrative and there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lots of travel, often exotic.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s financially lucrative and there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lots\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You work for yourself.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It beats most desk jobs.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most desk jobs\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But for Kerber, it was ultimately unsatisfying.\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerber\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For her first five or six years on tour, she was tracking for a fine career.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her first five or six years\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"tour\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"a fine career\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A converted lefty, she won her share of matches, even reaching the odd major semifinal.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her share\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"the odd major semifinal\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when she entered her mid-20s, her ranking had barely entered its mid-20s.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her mid-20s\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"her ranking\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"its mid-20s\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, the deluge.\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Then, the deluge\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerber changed coaches, got herself into peak shape, retooled her game to maximize her strengths (like speed) and minimize her weaknesses (like her second serve) \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 and the results came fast.\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"peak shape\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"her game\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"her strengths\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"speed\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"her weaknesses\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"her second serve) \\u00e2\\u0080\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a6\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same month she turned 28, she claimed her first major title, beating Serena Williams in a three-set final to win the 2016 Australian Open.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1259, \"end\": 1274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Serena Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her first major title\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"a three-set final\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Australian Open\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Wimbledon that year, she again reached the final, this time losing to Williams.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Less than a month later, she earned silver in women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s singles at the Rio Olympics.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rio Olympics\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1495}]}, {\"sentence\